 tu reserva de maná.£{RW}, {T}: Agrega {R}{R}, {R}{W}, o {W}{W} a tu reserva de maná.',NULL,'#_大精灵将亲人葬在远处。 他们相信在这种乾燥又广阔的地方，巫婆无法偷取遗骨，山妪不能窃走灵魂。_#',NULL,'#_Les lutins enterrent leurs morts loin de chez eux. Ils croient qu''un sol aride et dégagé empêche les mégères de voler les ossements et les gwyllion de voler les âmes._#','#_Hobgoblins begraben ihre Angehörigen fern der Heimat. Sie glauben, dass der trockene, offene Boden verhindert, dass Vetteln die Knochen und Gwyllion die Seelen stehlen._#','#_Gli hob seppelliscono i loro cari lontano da casa. Credono che il terreno arido e scoperto impedisca alle streghe di rubare le ossa e alle gwyllion di rubare gli spiriti._#','#_ホブは仲間を住処から遠くに埋葬する。 乾いた見晴らしのいい場所なら、ハッグが骨を盗んだり、グウィリオンが魂を盗んだりしないと信じているのだ。_#','#_Os hobs enterram os seus bem longe de casa. Eles acreditam que o solo seco e amplo impede que as bruxas roubem seus ossos e os gwyllions seus espíritos._#','#_Хобгоблины хоронят своих сородичей далеко от дома. Они считают, что на сухом и открытом пространстве карги-ведьмы не будут красть кости, а гвиллионы — духов._#','#_Los hobs entierran a los suyos lejos de casa. Creen que el terreno abierto y seco evita que las sagas roben sus huesos y las gwyllion roben sus espíritus._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('157204','Sanity Grinding','EVE','Sorcery','R','{U}{U}{U}','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_Chroma_# — Reveal the top ten cards of your library. For each blue mana symbol in the mana costs of the revealed cards, target opponent puts the top card of their library into their graveyard. Then put the cards you revealed this way on the bottom of your library in any order.',NULL,NULL,'Lars Grant-West','29','3.517','£8/1/2008: Chroma abilities check only mana costs, which are found in a card’s upper right corner. They don’t count mana symbols that appear in a card’s text box.£8/1/2008: Chroma abilities count hybrid mana symbols of the appropriate color. For example, a card with mana cost {3}{UR}{UR} has 